--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μέμφις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μέμφις\"><span data-text=\"Μέμφις\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Μέμφις\">ΜΕΜΦΙΣ</span></span></span></span><br id=\"aA-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεκένιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεκένιος\"><span data-text=\"Δεκένιος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Δεκένιος\">ΔΕΚΕΝΙΟΣ</span></span></span></span><span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span></span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abB\">section B</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divB--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aB-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>†<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τίτος ❦ Αἴλις Βικτωρεῖνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τίτος\"><span data-text=\"Τίτος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Τίτος\">ΤΙΤΟ.</span></span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Αἴλις\"><span data-text=\"Αἴλις\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Αἴλις\">ΑΙΛΙΣ</span></span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρεῖνος\"><span data-text=\"Βικτωρεῖνος\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Βικτωρεῖνος\">ΒΙΚΤΩΡΕΙΝΟΣ</span></span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΤΗ</span></span><span class=\"underline\">·</span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-text=\"ις\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ις\">ΙΣ</span></span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"μείς\"><span class=\"underline\">ΜΗΝΕΣ</span></span><span class=\"underline\">·</span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-text=\"ε\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ε\">Ε</span></span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\"><span class=\"underline\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span></span><span class=\"underline\"><span data-text=\"ιζ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"ιζ\">ΙΖ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἀδελφοὶ\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ἀδελφός\"><span class=\"underline\">ΑΔΕΛΦΟΙ</span></span><br id=\"aB-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"εὐσεβεῖς\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"εὐσεβής\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΥΣΕΒΕΙΣ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"σὺν\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"σύν\"><span class=\"underline\">ΣΥΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"μητρὶ\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"μήτηρ\"><span class=\"underline\">ΜΗΤΡΙ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἐκ\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἐκ\"><span class=\"underline\">ΕΚ</span></span><span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\"><span class=\"underline\">ΤΩΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"αὐτοῦ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\"><span class=\"underline\">ΑΥΤΟΥ</span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abA\">section A</span><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divA--diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Μέμφις\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Μέμφις\">ΜΕΜΦΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Δεκένιος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Δεκένιος\">ΔΕΚΕΝΙΟΣ</span></span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abB\">section B</span><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divB--diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Τίτος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Τίτος\">ΤΙΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Αἴλις\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Αἴλις\">ΑΙΛΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Βικτωρεῖνος\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Βικτωρεῖνος\">ΒΙΚΤΩΡΕΙΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ις\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ις\">ΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνες\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΕΣ</span><span data-text=\"ε\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"ε\">Ε</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ιζ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"ιζ\">ΙΖ</span><span data-text=\"ἀδελφοὶ\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ἀδελφός\">ΑΔΕΛΦΟΙ</span><span data-text=\"εὐσεβεῖς\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"εὐσεβής\">ΕΥΣΕΒΕΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ</span><span data-text=\"σὺν\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"σύν\">ΣΥΝ</span><span data-text=\"μητρὶ\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"μήτηρ\">ΜΗΤΡΙ</span><span data-text=\"ἐκ\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἐκ\">ΕΚ</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"αὐτοῦ\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\">ΑΥΤΟΥ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001346_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag\" src=\"ISic001346_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001346.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag\" src=\"ISic001346-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001346_rev_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag\" src=\"ISic001346_rev_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001346_rev.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag\" src=\"ISic001346_rev-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photograph and previous editors</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"B.1\">B.1: <span>Mommsen TITO S[-]ATAR/ae</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"B.1\">  <span>Walther, Amico, Torremuzza, Ferrara, Kirchhof, Ferrua, Korhonen: ἔτη ις´, μῆνες ε´; Kaibel, Wessel: ἔτη ις´ (vel ιγ´), μῆνες ε´ (vel θ´)</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"B.2\">B.2: <span>Walther, Amico, Torremuzza, Ferrara, Kirchhof, Ferrua, Korhonen: αὐτοῦ; Kaibel, Wessel: αὐτῶν</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Titus Aelius Victorinus lived 16 years, 5 months, 17 days. His dutiful brothers made (this) together with their mother from the legacy of Victorinus ...</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Titos Aelios Victorinos visse 18 anni, 5 mesi e 17 giorni. I suoi fratelli pietosi hanno realizzato (questo) insieme con la loro madre dagli averi di Vittorino ...</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Walther and Vallambert (in Cod. Vat. Lat. 6039 f. 85v) describe the relief, in which a bare-headed man with a long tunic was surrounded by two young boys, one riding a horse, the other leading another horse (the names of the boys were inscribed on the relief <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ΜΕΜΦΙΣ</span> and <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ΔΕΚΕΝΙΟΣ</span>, the latter written right to left). The epitaph was considered to be Christian by the editors before Ferrua because of the cross symbol before <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Τίτος</span>. However, the symbol has proven to be later, perhaps modern, since Vallambert in the mid-16th century did not see it. The cross may have been inscribed at a later stage to make the object “more Christian”. Apart from this, there is no other evidence for a Christian provenance of the inscription: the subject of the relief argues rather in favour of a pagan provenance of the document, as Ferrua remarks. The two naked young men near horses may refer to the Dioscuri, just as the expression <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἀδελφοὶ εὐσεβεῖς</span> may refer to another pair of brothers famous in Catania, the <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">Pii fratres</span>, named also in IG 14.502 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001323\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001323</a>. The grave could also have been built not by the brothers of the deceased, but “metaphorically” by the <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">Pii fratres</span>, that is by his mother under the protection of the divine brothers.</p>  <p>Korhonen favours a dating to the second half of the 2nd century CE because Titus Aelius was often adopted by freedmen after the reign of Antoninus Pius. For the expression <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐκ τῶν αὐτοῦ</span> as the equivalent of <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">sua pecunia</span>, see IG 14.574 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001393\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001393</a>.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 9211 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/310933\" target=\"_blank\">36</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Amico 1741 260 no.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 256 no.54 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 274 no.62 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 369 no.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9477 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">1063*</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">527</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1941 162-164 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 52 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Slightly irregularly disposed letters, with a hedera between the first two words. In the text preserved by Gualtherus lunate epsilon, sigma and cursive omega are recorded, and interpuncts before the numerals.</p> Line 1  30-37  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
